      "content": "but it doesn't help. i talk to people and they just tell me to \"hang in there\" or \"it gets better,\" but it never does. it just feels like a cycle of more stress and more failing. it honestly feels like the only way to actually stop the noise is to just... stop everything. it feels like the only logical way to get some peace.",
